Dialogue: 100,0:00:46.52,0:00:48.69,Default,Kobayashi,0,0,0,,Damn, talk about a hangover...
Dialogue: 100,0:00:48.69,0:00:50.53,Default,Kobayashi,0,0,0,,I drank way too much last night.{..}
Dialogue: 100,0:01:04.54,0:01:05.46,Default,Kobayashi,0,0,0,,It's freezing!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:07.13,0:01:09.38,Default,Maid,0,0,0,,Come visit Maid Café Cozy!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:09.38,0:01:11.34,Default,Maid,0,0,0,,Please stop by.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:11.34,0:01:13.38,Default,Maid,0,0,0,,We'd love to see you there!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:15.68,0:01:17.84,Default,Kobayashi,0,0,0,,Jeez, my back...
Dialogue: 100,0:01:20.35,0:01:24.56,Default,Kobayashi,0,0,0,,Today's the day we run the integration test on that program, huh?
Dialogue: 100,0:01:45.33,0:01:46.62,Default - Italic,Kobayashi,0,0,0,,Dragons.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:46.62,0:01:49.04,Default - Italic,Kobayashi,0,0,0,,The most powerful beings known to mankind.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:49.67,0:01:56.42,Default - Italic,Kobayashi,0,0,0,,Mythical creatures that breathe fire, fly, \Nand are sometimes said to have magic powers.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:59.89,0:02:02.43,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,Ta-da!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:10.19,0:02:12.98,Default - Italic,Kobayashi,0,0,0,,Or... so I thought.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:48.79,0:03:50.62,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,Good morning, Miss Kobayashi.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:55.79,0:03:57.00,Default,Kobayashi,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:57.38,0:03:59.38,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,Do you mind if I come inside?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:59.38,0:04:01.92,Default,Kobayashi,0,0,0,,Oh, sure, come on in.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:04.51,0:04:08.10,Default - Top,Kobayashi,0,0,0,,So you're telling me we met yesterday, and I offered to let you stay here?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:08.10,0:04:11.02,Default - Top,Kobayashi,0,0,0,,I told you that, uh... Tohru{-san}?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:11.39,0:04:12.52,Default - Top,Tohru,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:13.19,0:04:14.44,Default - Italic,K,0,0,0,Split,Hmm, weird.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:14.44,0:04:15.90,Default - Italic,K,0,0,0,Split,I'm not waking up for some reason.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:16.27,0:04:17.23,Default - Italic,K,0,0,0,,What if I'm not dreaming?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:18.02,0:04:19.28,Default - Italic,K,0,0,0,,Nah, there's no way.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:21.36,0:04:22.20,Default,K,0,0,0,,So, uh...
Dialogue: 100,0:04:22.20,0:04:23.86,Default,K,0,0,0,,Where did we meet?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:23.86,0:04:24.70,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,In the mountains!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:24.70,0:04:26.37,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,We met in the mountains!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:27.74,0:04:28.45,Default,K,0,0,0,,The mountains?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:30.75,0:04:31.95,Default,K,0,0,0,,Mountains...
Dialogue: 100,0:04:33.29,0:04:34.79,Default,K,0,0,0,,In the mountains...
Dialogue: 100,0:04:37.71,0:04:39.09,Default,K,0,0,0,,A dragon?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:40.59,0:04:41.76,Default,K,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 100,0:04:43.38,0:04:44.51,Default,K,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 100,0:04:48.18,0:04:50.26,Default,K,0,0,0,,Wanna come crash at my place?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:50.26,0:04:52.27,Default,K,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFE&\4a&H00&\shad0.1\t(3,\4a&HFF&\blur12)}Wanna come crash at my place?
Dialogue: 101,0:04:50.26,0:04:52.27,Default,K,0,0,0,,{\bord0\t(3,\alpha&HFE&\blur8)}Wanna come crash at my place?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:53.27,0:04:55.94,Default,T,0,0,0,,I'll never forget those kind words!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:56.73,0:05:00.07,Default,T,0,0,0,,Please let me work here as your maid!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:00.07,0:05:02.15,Default,K,0,0,0,,Thanks, but no thanks.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:02.49,0:05:04.90,Default,K,0,0,0,split,I don't really get this whole dragon thing,
Dialogue: 100,0:05:04.90,0:05:07.03,Default,K,0,0,0,Split,but I'm not planning on hiring anyone.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:08.41,0:05:10.16,Default,T,0,0,0,,Y-You don't even have to pay me!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:10.16,0:05:11.83,Default,K,0,0,0,,No, you're missing the{ point}—
Dialogue: 100,0:05:11.83,0:05:13.91,Default,T,0,0,0,,I'm useful to have around!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:14.16,0:05:15.83,Default,T,0,0,0,,I can create a vast sea of fire,
Dialogue: 100,0:05:15.83,0:05:17.29,Default,T,0,0,0,,or curse people to death!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:17.29,0:05:18.54,Default,K,0,0,0,,Nobody's asking for that!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:18.83,0:05:20.50,Default,K,0,0,0,,Anyway, why a maid?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:20.50,0:05:22.96,Default,T,0,0,0,,Because you told me you wanted a maid!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:23.21,0:05:24.47,Default,K,0,0,0,,Did I?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:28.93,0:05:30.85,Default,K,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:33.27,0:05:36.19,Default,K,0,0,0,,Well, I'm sorry for making \Na promise that I can't keep.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:36.48,0:05:38.44,Default,K,0,0,0,,But you've gotta understand.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:38.85,0:05:40.69,Default,K,0,0,0,,It's just not gonna work out.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:46.57,0:05:49.28,Default,T,0,0,0,,There's no way we can make it work?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:49.57,0:05:50.83,Default,K,0,0,0,Split,No.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:50.83,0:05:51.53,Default,K,0,0,0,Split,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:55.50,0:05:56.54,Default,T,0,0,0,,Okay, I understand.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:57.21,0:06:00.71,Default,T,0,0,0,,My apologies for dropping in so suddenly.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:14.35,0:06:16.60,Default,K,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFE&\4a&H00&\shad0.1\blur9\t(20,193,\blur0)}Wanna come crash at my place?
Dialogue: 101,0:06:14.35,0:06:16.60,Default,K,0,0,0,,{\bord0\blur5\t(20,193,\blur0)}Wanna come crash at my place?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:18.44,0:06:20.48,Default - Italic,K,0,0,0,,I can't shake this feeling of guilt.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:24.19,0:06:26.32,Default - Italic,K,0,0,0,,Wait, what if this isn't a dream?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:27.15,0:06:29.99,Default - Italic,K,0,0,0,,If that's the case, then...
Dialogue: 100,0:06:34.08,0:06:34.83,Default,K,0,0,0,,I'm late!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:35.24,0:06:36.16,Default,K,0,0,0,,Tohru!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:40.00,0:06:40.71,Default,K,0,0,0,,Can you fly?!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:51.09,0:06:52.97,Default,K,0,0,0,,Whoa, you're fast!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:52.97,0:06:54.43,Default,Dragon,0,0,0,,Huh? What was that?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:54.43,0:06:56.47,Default,K,0,0,0,,You're really damn fast!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:02.36,0:07:03.11,Default,K,0,0,0,,Guess I'll hire her.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:03.11,0:07:04.44,Default,D,0,0,0,,You mean it?!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:04.44,0:07:05.86,Default,K,0,0,0,,So {\i1}now{\i0} you can hear me.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:08.94,0:07:12.91,Default - Italic,K,0,0,0,,You know, I can't honestly say I hate the idea of having someone around.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:12.91,0:07:13.53,Default - Italic,K,0,0,0,,I might even—
Dialogue: 100,0:07:15.74,0:07:18.70,Default - Italic,K,0,0,0,,This is gonna kill my back.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:22.12,0:07:23.13,Default,K,0,0,0,,Ahem.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:23.63,0:07:28.21,Default,K,0,0,0,,All right, let's see{show me} what you \Nthink being a maid is all about.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:28.21,0:07:29.38,Default,T,0,0,0,,Very well!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:29.72,0:07:30.76,Default,T,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:31.26,0:07:33.22,Default,T,0,0,0,,Come visit Maid Café Cozy!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:34.01,0:07:35.14,Default,K,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:35.14,0:07:37.56,Default,T,0,0,0,,I saw it on the way here.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:37.56,0:07:39.77,Default,K,0,0,0,,Looks like we're gonna have to start from scratch.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:40.02,0:07:42.40,Default,K,0,0,0,,First, as a housemaid, you clean!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:42.40,0:07:43.90,Default,T,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm good at cleaning!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:47.19,0:07:47.86,Default,T,0,0,0,,How's that?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:47.86,0:07:48.94,Default,K,0,0,0,,Where'd all my stuff go?!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:48.94,0:07:49.99,Default,T,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll bring it back.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:49.99,0:07:50.95,Default,K,0,0,0,,You can do that?!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:50.95,0:07:52.95,Default,K,0,0,0,,Next, laundry maid!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:52.95,0:07:53.86,Default,K,0,0,0,,The name says it all.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:53.86,0:07:55.45,Default,T,0,0,0,,I can handle that too!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:56.83,0:08:00.33,Default,T/Screen,0,0,10,,{\q2}I can produce saliva that eliminates all stains.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:00.33,0:08:02.33,Default,K,0,0,10,,That's gross! Presentation is vital!{Keeping up appearances is rule #1!}
Dialogue: 100,0:08:02.67,0:08:04.17,Default,K,0,0,0,,Next, parlor maid!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:04.17,0:08:05.29,Default,K,0,0,0,,You receive visitors.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:05.29,0:08:06.63,Default,T,0,0,0,,No problem!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:07.29,0:08:09.63,Default,Delivery,0,0,0,,Delivery. Could I get your signature, please?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:09.63,0:08:12.68,Default,T,0,0,0,,We have nothing for foolish, \Ninferior{this exact phrase gets used in the ED. c'MON, ddy} humans like you!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:12.68,0:08:13.51,Default,K,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 100,0:08:13.51,0:08:16.14,Default,T,0,0,0,,Oh, you're an exception of course, Miss Kobayashi!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:16.14,0:08:18.51,Default,K,0,0,0,,And last but not least, kitchen maid!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:18.51,0:08:19.31,Default,K,0,0,0,,You cook!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:19.31,0:08:21.02,Default,T,0,0,0,,Cooking is my strongest of strong points!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:21.98,0:08:24.15,Default,T,0,0,0,,It's my tail, fried to perfection!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:24.15,0:08:25.27,Default,K,0,0,0,,Yeah, no.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:26.52,0:08:27.23,Default,K,0,0,0,,Not happening.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:27.23,0:08:28.11,Default,T,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:28.11,0:08:30.44,Default,T,0,0,0,,Should I have fried it longer?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:30.44,0:08:31.49,Default,K,0,0,0,,That's not the problem.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:31.49,0:08:33.65,Default,T,0,0,0,,I'm confident you'll enjoy it, Miss Kobayashi!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:33.65,0:08:35.45,Default,K,0,0,0,,My stomach and conscience sure won't.{Sriram Gurunathan GOAT}
Dialogue: 100,0:08:35.45,0:08:38.16,Default,T,0,0,0,,Oh, I see. So you're a picky eater, then?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:38.16,0:08:39.12,Default,K,0,0,0,,Maybe to you.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:39.12,0:08:42.62,Default,T,0,0,0,,Jeez, you're hopeless.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:45.79,0:08:46.75,Default,K,0,0,0,,It grew back?!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:46.75,0:08:49.30,Default,T,0,0,0,,I went through a lot of trouble \Nto remove the poison, you know!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:49.30,0:08:50.13,Default,K,0,0,0,,It's poisonous?!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:52.26,0:08:55.13,Default,K,0,0,0,,You don't even know the first thing about being a maid.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:55.13,0:08:56.68,Default,T,0,0,0,,I'll learn on the job!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:56.68,0:08:59.81,Default,T,0,0,0,,Let's start with telling me what you dislike.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:59.81,0:09:01.39,Default,K,0,0,0,,What I dislike?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:01.39,0:09:03.35,Default,K,0,0,0,,I'm can't stand seaweed{hijiki} or eggplant.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:03.35,0:09:05.27,Default,T,0,0,0,,I see. I'll keep that in mind.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:05.81,0:09:09.06,Default,T,0,0,0,,As for me, I'm not fond of eggs without yolks.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:09.06,0:09:11.98,Default,T,0,0,0,,My friend Herensuge was slain using one.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:11.98,0:09:13.65,Default,K,0,0,0,,That's surreal.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:13.99,0:09:16.49,Default,K,0,0,0,,Wait, why are you asking me what I dislike?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:16.49,0:09:18.32,Default,K,0,0,0,,Wouldn't you normally ask what I like?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:18.32,0:09:20.12,Default,T,0,0,0,,Oh, I can't do that.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:20.62,0:09:24.41,Default,T,0,0,0,,Many of my friends were slain after having the things they liked used against them.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:24.41,0:09:26.79,Default,T,0,0,0,,Liquor, women, precious stones... \NThat sort of thing.{COULD cut out second part entirely. unsure.}
Dialogue: 100,0:09:26.79,0:09:28.38,Default,K,0,0,0,,Not too different from humans.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:28.83,0:09:31.46,Default,T,0,0,0,,But I'll let you in on just this one thing!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:31.46,0:09:33.88,Default,T,0,0,0,,I love you, Miss Kobayashi!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:35.05,0:09:35.84,Default,K,0,0,0,,Am I your next meal?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:35.84,0:09:38.05,Default,T,0,0,0,,Not in that sense! I mean sexually!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:38.05,0:09:39.72,Default,K,0,0,0,,You know I'm a woman, right?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:40.14,0:09:42.68,Default,T,0,0,0,,You saved me, Miss Kobayashi!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:42.68,0:09:45.98,Default,T,0,0,0,,I must repay your kindness \Nwith my entire being!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:45.98,0:09:48.48,Default,T,0,0,0,,I'd like you to use me to commute to work again tomorrow!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:48.48,0:09:51.52,Default,K,0,0,0,,I had enough of that \Nfor a lifetime today. You're too much.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:51.52,0:09:53.44,Default,T,0,0,0,,Please give me a chance!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:53.44,0:09:58.53,Default,T,0,0,0,,I was raised to repay all debts, \Neven {when owed }to foolish, inferior humans!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:58.53,0:10:01.12,Default,K,0,0,0,,Again with the "foolish and inferior" thing.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:01.87,0:10:03.08,Default,K,0,0,0,Split,Look, Tohru.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:03.08,0:10:06.16,Default,K,0,0,0,Split,There's a reason I won't use you to commute.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:06.16,0:10:07.29,Default,T,0,0,0,,Your back?
Dialogue: 100,0:10:07.29,0:10:08.62,Default,K,0,0,0,,That's part of it.{That's half the reason.}
Dialogue: 100,0:10:09.12,0:10:12.13,Default,K,0,0,0,,But, more importantly...{The other half is...}
Dialogue: 100,0:10:12.50,0:10:14.30,Default,K,0,0,0,,You stand out!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:14.30,0:10:17.22,Default,K,0,0,0,,I think dragons are better left holding {down }the fort!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:17.22,0:10:18.63,Default,T,0,0,0,,H-Holding the fort?
Dialogue: 100,0:10:19.13,0:10:21.35,Default,K,0,0,0,,You're one of the stronger dragons, right, Tohru?
Dialogue: 100,0:10:21.35,0:10:23.47,Default,T,0,0,0,,Strong enough to bring about Armageddon.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:23.47,0:10:24.64,Default,K,0,0,0,,Yeah, let's not do that.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:25.06,0:10:28.27,Default,K,0,0,0,,The world's been a dangerous place lately.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:28.27,0:10:32.06,Default,K,0,0,0,,It'd put my mind at ease to know \Nyou're here keeping the house safe.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:32.73,0:10:36.03,Default,T,0,0,0,combined,Very well! You can count on me!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:36.03,0:10:37.15,Default,K,0,0,0,,Duh-ragon.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:37.49,0:10:39.41,Default,K,0,0,0,,Well, I'm off to the office.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:40.07,0:10:42.70,Default,K,0,0,0,,If the phone rings, please answer.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:42.70,0:10:43.70,Default,T,0,0,0,,Phone?
Dialogue: 100,0:10:43.70,0:10:45.12,Default,K,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:45.41,0:10:46.62,Default,K,0,0,0,,This is a phone.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:46.87,0:10:49.79,Default,K,0,0,0,,When it rings, pick it up like this.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:49.79,0:10:50.88,Default,K,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 100,0:10:51.17,0:10:52.38,Default,T,0,0,0,,Understood!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:52.38,0:10:53.29,Default,K,0,0,0,,Okay, take care.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:53.29,0:10:54.75,Default,T,0,0,0,,Have a safe trip!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:56.80,0:10:57.76,Default,T,0,0,0,,Holding the fort?
Dialogue: 100,0:11:01.43,0:11:03.51,Default,T,0,0,0,,What were those humans doing, anyway?
Dialogue: 100,0:11:04.26,0:11:06.52,Default,T,0,0,0,,I guess I can ask Fafnir{-san}.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:07.39,0:11:08.52,Default - Italic,Fafnir,0,0,0,,Kill them.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:09.02,0:11:11.81,Default - Italic,Fafnir,0,0,0,,Kill all who try to steal your treasure.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:11.81,0:11:13.31,Default - Italic,Fafnir,0,0,0,,Kill all you suspect.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:13.31,0:11:14.94,Default - Italic,Fafnir,0,0,0,,Curse them to death.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:14.94,0:11:16.15,Default - Italic,Fafnir,0,0,0,,Curse their descendants and—
Dialogue: 100,0:11:16.15,0:11:18.03,Default,T,0,0,0,,Wow, that was enlightening!
Dialogue: 100,0:11:18.03,0:11:22.53,Default,T,0,0,0,,All right, time to do my best \Nto earn Miss Kobayashi's praise!
Dialogue: 100,0:11:25.53,0:11:28.62,Default,Thief,0,0,0,,This tenant's always out around this time of day.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:28.62,0:11:30.50,Default,Thief,0,0,0,,Easy job, in and out.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:45.55,0:11:47.06,Default,Thief,0,0,0,,You gotta help us!
Dialogue: 100,0:11:47.43,0:11:48.31,Default,Thief,0,0,0,,We saw one!
Dialogue: 100,0:11:48.31,0:11:48.81,Default,Police,0,0,0,,Saw what?
Dialogue: 100,0:11:48.81,0:11:50.18,Default,Thief,0,0,0,,A monster!
Dialogue: 100,0:11:50.94,0:11:52.27,Default,K,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:52.27,0:11:53.77,Default,T,0,0,0,,Welcome home!
Dialogue: 100,0:11:53.77,0:11:55.02,Default,K,0,0,0,,How'd holding {down }the fort go?
Dialogue: 100,0:11:55.02,0:11:57.02,Default,T,0,0,0,,I was lonely all by myself.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:57.02,0:11:59.07,Default,T,0,0,0,,I didn't even get to kill them.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:59.07,0:11:59.94,Default,K,0,0,0,Split,Wait, what?
Dialogue: 100,0:12:13.42,0:12:14.58,Default,Takiya,0,0,0,,Kobayashi{-san}.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:14.96,0:12:16.54,Default - Top,K,0,0,0,,What's up, Takiya{-kun}?
Dialogue: 100,0:12:16.54,0:12:18.09,Default - Top,M,0,0,0,,Wanna hit the bar tonight?
Dialogue: 100,0:12:18.50,0:12:20.76,Default,K,0,0,0,,Well, I guess I could go for a round.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:22.80,0:12:25.43,Default,K,0,0,0,,There are plenty of other girls you could ask, you know.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:25.43,0:12:28.64,Default,M,0,0,0,,Yeah, but you're like one of the guys.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:28.64,0:12:30.47,Default,K,0,0,0,,Why you...
Dialogue: 100,0:12:32.18,0:12:34.98,Default,M,0,0,0,,That girl's looking our way. You know her?
Dialogue: 100,0:12:37.36,0:12:39.78,Default,T,0,0,0,,I'm Kobayashi Tohru!
Dialogue: 100,0:12:39.78,0:12:44.32,Default,T,0,0,0,,A maid who spends {\i1}every day{\i0} living with Miss Kobayashi.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:45.36,0:12:48.28,Default,K,0,0,0,,She's a relative of mine I'm looking after right now.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:48.28,0:12:51.70,Default,M,0,0,0,,I'm Takiya Makoto, her coworker.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:51.70,0:12:53.46,Default,M,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you, Tohru{-chan}.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:53.46,0:12:55.21,Default,T,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you too.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:55.92,0:12:58.71,Default - Top,M,0,0,0,,We were just talking about going out for drinks together.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:56.17,0:12:59.96,Default - Italic,T,0,0,0,,This man is trying to seduce Miss Kobayashi.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:58.71,0:12:59.96,Default - Top,M,0,0,0,,Care to join us?
Dialogue: 100,0:12:59.96,0:13:02.21,Default - Top,M,0,0,0,,Actually, are you old enough to drink?
Dialogue: 100,0:13:00.80,0:13:02.21,Default - Italic,T,0,0,0,,Not on my watch, you don't!
Dialogue: 100,0:13:02.21,0:13:04.72,Default,T,0,0,0,,Yes, I can drink, stultus.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:05.55,0:13:06.47,Default,M,0,0,0,,Stul...?
Dialogue: 100,0:13:11.77,0:13:14.18,Default,K,0,0,0,,Nothing beats a round after work!
Dialogue: 100,0:13:14.64,0:13:16.44,Default - Italic,T,0,0,0,,Miss Kobayashi's so cute!
Dialogue: 100,0:13:16.44,0:13:19.36,Default,M,0,0,0,,Oh? Not having any alcohol, Tohru{-chan}?
Dialogue: 100,0:13:19.36,0:13:19.94,Default,T,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:20.27,0:13:23.19,Default - Top,M,0,0,0,,I see. Well, I guess I can't tell you what to drink.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:20.27,0:13:23.19,Default - Italic,T,0,0,0,,As if I would ever drink with the likes of you.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:23.19,0:13:25.49,Default - Italic,T,0,0,0,,Still, what do I do about this man?
Dialogue: 100,0:13:25.49,0:13:28.32,Default - Italic,T,0,0,0,,This world's laws are too strict \Nto do anything drastic.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:28.32,0:13:29.32,Default - Italic,T,0,0,0,,Oh, I know!
Dialogue: 100,0:13:29.78,0:13:33.45,Default - Top,M,0,0,0,,Man, {still, }today's work was rough, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 100,0:13:30.20,0:13:33.45,Default - Italic,T,0,0,0,,All I have to do is show off how close the two of us are!
Dialogue: 100,0:13:33.45,0:13:37.46,Default,K,0,0,0,,We're at the bottom of two or three layers \Nof subcontracting. What do you expect?
Dialogue: 100,0:13:37.75,0:13:41.71,Default,M,0,0,0,,But whenever we do things their way, \Nit always ends up causing bugs.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:41.71,0:13:44.47,Default,M,0,0,0,,And if we don't point them out, \Nthe devs never fix{do anything about} 'em.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:44.47,0:13:48.84,Default,K,0,0,0,,So what? That's exactly \Nwhat we're getting paid for.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:48.84,0:13:52.85,Default,M,0,0,0,,I mean, yeah, but that doesn't make it \Nany less of a pain in the ass.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:52.85,0:13:55.68,Default - Top,K,0,0,0,,It's common practice for schedules to be based on people taking on extra roles.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:55.68,0:13:57.31,Default - Top,K,0,0,0,,Common practice!
Dialogue: 100,0:13:53.27,0:13:55.93,Default - Italic,T,0,0,0,,I can't follow this conversation at all!
Dialogue: 100,0:13:55.93,0:13:57.31,Default - Italic,T,0,0,0,,Could I get that in Dragonese{, please}?
Dialogue: 100,0:13:57.31,0:13:59.48,Default,M,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm sorry, Tohru{-chan}.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:59.81,0:14:02.73,Default,M,0,0,0,,It must be hard for you to join in this conversation.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:03.19,0:14:06.07,Default,T,0,0,0,,N-No! It's just so low-level \NI don't feel like joining in, that's all!
Dialogue: 100,0:14:06.07,0:14:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, right...
Dialogue: 100,0:14:07.03,0:14:10.32,Default,T,0,0,0,,Why don't we talk about \NRagnarok or Armageddon instead?
Dialogue: 100,0:14:10.32,0:14:11.08,Default,M,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 100,0:14:11.37,0:14:13.24,Default,T,0,0,0,,Never mind that. I've had enough of this!
Dialogue: 100,0:14:13.24,0:14:14.37,Default,T,0,0,0,,You leave me no choice!
Dialogue: 100,0:14:14.37,0:14:16.79,Default,T,0,0,0,,I'll kill you and leave you{r corpse} out to feed the jackals!
Dialogue: 100,0:14:19.21,0:14:20.33,Default,T,0,0,0,,Miss Kobayashi?
Dialogue: 100,0:14:23.13,0:14:25.67,Default,K,0,0,0,,Tohru!
Dialogue: 100,0:14:25.92,0:14:30.43,Default,K,0,0,0,,A maid would never talk like that!
Dialogue: 100,0:14:30.43,0:14:31.43,Default,T,0,0,0,,She's drunk?!
Dialogue: 100,0:14:31.43,0:14:34.01,Default,K,0,0,0,,First of all, what's with your maid uniform?
Dialogue: 100,0:14:34.01,0:14:35.39,Default,K,0,0,0,,Are you a maid or a parody?
Dialogue: 100,0:14:35.39,0:14:37.18,Default,K,0,0,0,,Braid your hair and put it in a cap.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:37.18,0:14:40.19,Default,K,0,0,0,,The world's got enough French maids. You're basically just cosplaying.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:40.19,0:14:42.23,Default,Makoto,0,0,0,,Here it comes!
Dialogue: 100,0:14:42.23,0:14:43.65,Default,T,0,0,0,,{Mr. }T-Takiya{-san}?!
Dialogue: 100,0:14:43.65,0:14:45.03,Default,M,0,0,0,,Madam Kobayashi!
Dialogue: 100,0:14:45.03,0:14:47.57,Default,M,0,0,0,,Tohru{-tan}'s maid level is indeed no better than cosplay!
Dialogue: 100,0:14:47.57,0:14:50.36,Default,M,0,0,0,,She's just like those foreigners pretending to be ninja or samurai!
Dialogue: 100,0:14:50.36,0:14:51.53,Default,K,0,0,0,,Damn right!
Dialogue: 100,0:14:51.53,0:14:53.91,Default,K,0,0,0,,I'll acknowledge the cuteness of the Gothic Lolita trend,
Dialogue: 100,0:14:53.91,0:14:56.83,Default,K,0,0,0,,but it's just a local fad, \Nnot proper formal attire!
Dialogue: 100,0:14:56.83,0:14:58.37,Default,M,0,0,0,Split,Now you're speaking my language!
Dialogue: 100,0:14:58.37,0:15:00.79,Default,M,0,0,0,Split,While Lolita and maid fashion may lend to one another,
Dialogue: 100,0:15:00.79,0:15:03.84,Default,M,0,0,0,,they should be more careful about blending together!
Dialogue: 100,0:15:03.84,0:15:08.09,Default - Top,M,0,0,0,,In the first place, maid costumes like hers spread throughout Japan because...
Dialogue: 100,0:15:04.63,0:15:08.09,Default - Italic,T,0,0,0,,This has gone way past simply joining \Nin the conversation or not.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:08.34,0:15:10.34,Default,K,0,0,0,,Hey, Tohru!
Dialogue: 100,0:15:10.80,0:15:16.14,Default,K,0,0,0,,We're giving you some high-level maid discussion, \Nso speak up, would ya?
Dialogue: 100,0:15:16.14,0:15:17.56,Default,T,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:17.85,0:15:22.10,Default,M,0,0,0,,Those horns of yours only bring you closer to the realm of cosplay.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:22.10,0:15:24.73,Default,T,0,0,0,,I'm just a dragon. \NI have no idea what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:24.73,0:15:25.48,Default,K,0,0,0,,Strip.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:25.73,0:15:26.23,Default,Both,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 100,0:15:26.23,0:15:28.03,Default,K,0,0,0,,Strip!
Dialogue: 100,0:15:28.78,0:15:29.40,Default,T,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 100,0:15:29.40,0:15:30.57,Default,K,0,0,0,,Hide them!
Dialogue: 100,0:15:30.57,0:15:31.95,Default,K,0,0,0,,Hide your breasts and loins!
Dialogue: 100,0:15:31.95,0:15:35.08,Default,K,0,0,0,,Acting embarrassed when exposed \Nis part of proper etiquette!
Dialogue: 100,0:15:35.08,0:15:35.99,Default,T,0,0,0,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 100,0:15:37.37,0:15:39.16,Default,K,0,0,0,,You call that embarrassed?!
Dialogue: 100,0:15:39.45,0:15:41.04,Default,K,0,0,0,,Show us what you're made of!
Dialogue: 100,0:15:41.54,0:15:43.71,Default - Italic,T,0,0,0,,H-Humans are terrifying!
Dialogue: 100,0:15:41.54,0:15:44.71,Default - Top,K,0,0,0,,Awwright! Bring on the liquor and maids!
Dialogue: 100,0:15:44.71,0:15:47.50,Default - Top,K,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1388)}Better make 'em Victorian too!
Dialogue: 100,0:15:47.63,0:15:49.30,Default,M,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Tohru{-chan}.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:49.67,0:15:53.05,Default,M,0,0,0,,I've made a habit of going drinking \Nwith Kobayashi{-san} to chat about maids.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:53.59,0:15:58.27,Default,M,0,0,0,,I'm a closet otaku, \Nso these outings are very precious to me.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:58.27,0:16:00.06,Default,T,0,0,0,,Yeah, I picked up that much.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:00.39,0:16:02.98,Default,T,0,0,0,,In exchange, I'll be giving you \Na little surprise of my own.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:18.33,0:16:20.50,Default,M,0,0,0,,We'll just say I drank too much.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:20.95,0:16:23.50,Default,M,0,0,0,,You really love Kobayashi{-san}, huh?
Dialogue: 100,0:16:24.71,0:16:25.88,Default,T,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:27.63,0:16:30.21,Default,T,0,0,0,,Though I have to say I hate you.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:52.15,0:16:56.07,Default,T,0,0,0,,So all humans soil their clothes with perspiration, huh?
Dialogue: 100,0:16:57.20,0:16:58.58,Default,T,0,0,0,,Silly lowborn species!
Dialogue: 100,0:16:59.91,0:17:01.79,Default,T,0,0,0,,Miss Kobayashi's sweat...
Dialogue: 100,0:17:03.66,0:17:06.50,Default,T,0,0,0,,Aw, it's all gone.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:07.42,0:17:09.29,Default,K,0,0,0,,How many times do I need to tell you?
Dialogue: 100,0:17:09.29,0:17:11.71,Default,K,0,0,0,,Stop licking the laundry.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:11.71,0:17:12.42,Default,T,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:12.67,0:17:14.38,Default,T,0,0,0,,From now on, I'll {just }lick you directly inst—
Dialogue: 100,0:17:14.38,0:17:15.30,Default,K,0,0,0,,Don't lick me either!
Dialogue: 100,0:17:15.30,0:17:17.05,Default,K,0,0,0,,Also, the way you do laundry...{is a problem too!}
Dialogue: 100,0:17:17.39,0:17:18.51,Default,T,0,0,0,,Am I doing something wrong?
Dialogue: 100,0:17:18.51,0:17:19.89,Default,K,0,0,0,,You are!
Dialogue: 100,0:17:19.89,0:17:21.72,Default,K,0,0,0,,Try listing the steps for doing laundry.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:21.72,0:17:22.31,Default,T,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 100,0:17:22.68,0:17:25.85,Default,T,0,0,0,,First, I use my clairvoyance to check inside your pockets.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:25.85,0:17:26.44,Default,K,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:26.69,0:17:29.90,Default,T,0,0,0,,Then, I wash the whites and the colors separately{, using separate detergents}.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:26.98,0:17:29.90,Default - Top,T,0,0,0,,Hurry up and finish!
Dialogue: 100,0:17:29.90,0:17:30.94,Default,K,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:31.23,0:17:32.78,Default,T,0,0,0,,Next, I wash the delicates by mouth.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:32.78,0:17:33.94,Default,K,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 100,0:17:33.94,0:17:35.82,Default,T,0,0,0,,I told you, I can produce saliva that eliminates all—
Dialogue: 100,0:17:35.82,0:17:38.24,Default,K,0,0,0,,Who cares? Like I said, presentation is important!
Dialogue: 100,0:17:38.24,0:17:39.95,Default,T,0,0,0,,Oh, you want me to make a show of it?
Dialogue: 100,0:17:39.95,0:17:41.70,Default,K,0,0,0,,That's not the problem here!
Dialogue: 100,0:17:41.99,0:17:43.20,Default,K,0,0,0,,Speaking of laundry, Tohru...
Dialogue: 100,0:17:43.20,0:17:45.41,Default,K,0,0,0,,Have you been wearing that same uniform this whole time?
Dialogue: 100,0:17:45.41,0:17:47.29,Default,K,0,0,0,,That won't do. You have to change at some point.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:47.29,0:17:48.96,Default,T,0,0,0,,But these are made out of my scales.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:48.96,0:17:50.09,Default,K,0,0,0,,Your scales?!
Dialogue: 100,0:17:50.09,0:17:53.05,Default,T,0,0,0,,That's right, so I don't need to change.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:53.76,0:17:55.26,Default,K,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:56.01,0:17:57.43,Default,T,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 100,0:17:58.39,0:18:00.01,Default,K,0,0,0,,Oh, whatever.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:00.30,0:18:02.26,Default,K,0,0,0,,I bought you some casual clothes either way.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:06.10,0:18:07.85,Default,T,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 100,0:18:07.85,0:18:11.82,Default,K,0,0,0,,Well, you're doing a lot for me, \Nso I wanted to show my thanks.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:11.82,0:18:12.73,Default,T,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 100,0:18:12.73,0:18:16.19,Default,T,0,0,0,,Miss Kobayashi, would you like a sacrifice later?
Dialogue: 100,0:18:16.19,0:18:17.86,Default,T,0,0,0,,Would you like to drink my fresh blood?
Dialogue: 100,0:18:17.86,0:18:18.99,Default,K,0,0,0,,What am I, a demon?!
Dialogue: 100,0:18:18.99,0:18:21.74,Default,T,0,0,0,,Heavens no! You're an angel!
Dialogue: 100,0:18:21.74,0:18:24.20,Default,T,0,0,0,,Oh, but please don't start serving God.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:24.20,0:18:25.45,Default,K,0,0,0,,Just try them on.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:26.50,0:18:28.12,Default,T,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 100,0:18:29.21,0:18:29.96,Default,K,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 100,0:18:29.96,0:18:31.25,Default,T,0,0,0,,The chest's a bit...
Dialogue: 100,0:18:31.71,0:18:33.38,Default,K,0,0,0,,Tohru, what's your cup size?
Dialogue: 100,0:18:33.38,0:18:35.38,Default,T,0,0,0,,D! D is for dragon!
Dialogue: 100,0:18:35.38,0:18:37.72,Default,K,0,0,0,,There you go learning stupid things.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:38.01,0:18:39.72,Default,K,0,0,0,,Oh, would you look at the time.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:40.34,0:18:41.47,Default,K,0,0,0,,Well, Tohru,
Dialogue: 100,0:18:41.47,0:18:45.39,Default,K,0,0,0,,use the Internet to study up on \Nhygiene practices until I get home.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:45.39,0:18:46.43,Default,T,0,0,0,,The Internet?
Dialogue: 100,0:18:46.43,0:18:47.60,Default,K,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:49.73,0:18:51.10,Default,T,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 100,0:18:51.36,0:18:52.77,Default,K,0,0,0,,You look things up like this.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:52.77,0:18:53.86,Default,T,0,0,0,,Understood!
Dialogue: 100,0:18:53.86,0:18:55.61,Default,K,0,0,0,,All right, I'm heading off.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:55.61,0:18:56.94,Default,T,0,0,0,,Have a safe trip.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:00.78,0:19:02.16,Default,T,0,0,0,,Now, then.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:06.95,0:19:10.54,Default,T,0,0,0,,Hmm, I still don't quite get it.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:11.88,0:19:14.67,Default,T,0,0,0,,I'll try asking Fafnir{-san} again.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:14.67,0:19:15.17,Default - Italic,F,0,0,0,,Kill th—
Dialogue: 100,0:19:15.67,0:19:16.92,Default,T,0,0,0,,Maybe not, actually.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:18.05,0:19:21.22,Default,T,0,0,0,,I'll ask Quetzalcoatl{-san} instead. \NShe knows a lot about these things.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:21.89,0:19:23.51,Default,T,0,0,0,,Hello, Lucoa{-san}?
Dialogue: 100,0:19:23.51,0:19:25.68,Default - Italic,L,0,0,0,,Tohru{-kun}? It's been a while.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:26.01,0:19:28.06,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,You see, blah blah, yadda yadda.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:30.44,0:19:33.69,Default - Italic,L,0,0,0,,That's not a simple matter of clean or dirty.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:34.19,0:19:36.07,Default - Italic,L,0,0,0,,You remember Nidhogg{-kun}, right?
Dialogue: 100,0:19:36.07,0:19:37.86,Default,T,0,0,0,,The one who's always gnawing on that tree's roots?
Dialogue: 100,0:19:37.86,0:19:39.49,Default - Italic,Lucua,0,0,0,,The world tree's, yeah.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:39.49,0:19:42.95,Default - Italic,Lucua,0,0,0,,No matter how much Nidhogg{-kun}'s venomous fangs corrupt it,
Dialogue: 100,0:19:42.95,0:19:46.74,Default - Italic,Lucua,0,0,0,,the goddesses purify it, \Nso the tree remains clean.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:46.74,0:19:47.70,Default,T,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:48.04,0:19:50.50,Default - Italic,L,0,0,0,,But what happens to the spots he gnaws?
Dialogue: 100,0:19:50.50,0:19:51.46,Default,T,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 100,0:19:51.46,0:19:54.67,Default,T,0,0,0,,I think he still leaves something behind. \NA curse or something.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:54.67,0:19:56.29,Default - Italic,L,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:56.29,0:19:59.13,Default - Italic,L,0,0,0,,This Miss Kobayashi you speak of must be worried about the same thing.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:59.13,0:20:01.47,Default,T,0,0,0,,I think I get it! \NThanks a bundle!{will change if brought up by any QCer}
Dialogue: 100,0:20:01.47,0:20:02.72,Default - Italic,L,0,0,0,,Tohru{-kun},
Dialogue: 100,0:20:03.09,0:20:05.51,Default - Italic,L,0,0,0,,are you enjoying life among humans?
Dialogue: 100,0:20:08.47,0:20:09.39,Default,T,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 100,0:20:14.73,0:20:18.53,Default,T,0,0,0,,The laundry isn't going to dry like this, is it?
Dialogue: 100,0:20:19.03,0:20:20.53,Default,T,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:49.81,0:20:51.27,Default,K,0,0,0,,C'mon, Tohru...
Dialogue: 100,0:20:51.77,0:20:54.27,Default,K,0,0,0,,Looks like she's{you've} still got a lot to learn.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:55.10,0:20:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 100,0:20:56.02,0:20:57.98,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,That breath...
Dialogue: 100,0:20:57.98,0:20:59.15,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,I found you.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:08.37,0:21:10.95,Default,T,0,0,0,,Nothing wrong with a bit of smelling, right?
Dialogue: 100,0:21:15.75,0:21:17.50,Default,K,0,0,0,,You don't need to sleep?
Dialogue: 100,0:21:17.50,0:21:18.38,Default,T,0,0,0,Split,No.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:18.38,0:21:21.38,Default,T,0,0,0,Split,But I want to sleep with you, so I will anyway!
Dialogue: 100,0:21:21.38,0:21:23.01,Default,K,0,0,0,,Well, whatever makes you happy.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:23.01,0:21:24.88,Default,T,0,0,0,,And make me happy it shall!
Dialogue: 100,0:21:27.39,0:21:29.10,Default,K,0,0,0,,Well, good night.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:29.10,0:21:31.10,Default,T,0,0,0,,Yes, good night.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:41.32,0:21:42.44,Default,K,0,0,0,,It's cramped.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:43.90,0:21:45.07,Default,T,0,0,0,,Should I get out?
Dialogue: 100,0:21:45.40,0:21:46.57,Default,K,0,0,0,,Nah, it's fine.
Dialogue: 100,0:22:33.54,0:22:34.74,Default,K,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 100,0:22:36.04,0:22:38.79,Default,T,0,0,0,,I was fighting. Back in my home world.
Dialogue: 100,0:22:39.37,0:22:41.92,Default,T,0,0,0,,A sword ran through my body.
Dialogue: 100,0:22:43.75,0:22:45.05,Default,K,0,0,0,,Did it hurt?
Dialogue: 100,0:22:45.51,0:22:46.80,Default,T,0,0,0,,It hurt.
Dialogue: 100,0:22:47.34,0:22:48.55,Default,K,0,0,0,,Does it still hurt?
Dialogue: 100,0:22:48.97,0:22:51.47,Default,T,0,0,0,,No, it doesn't hurt anymore.
Dialogue: 100,0:22:51.47,0:22:53.05,Default,K,0,0,0,,All's well, then.
Dialogue: 100,0:22:53.72,0:22:54.56,Default,K,0,0,0,,Good night.
Dialogue: 100,0:22:59.60,0:23:00.81,Default,T,0,0,0,,Good night.
Dialogue: 100,0:23:15.08,0:23:17.45,Default,T,0,0,0,,Welcome home, Miss Kobayashi.
Dialogue: 100,0:23:17.79,0:23:19.21,Default,T,0,0,0,,I've been awaiting your return.
Dialogue: 100,0:23:19.58,0:23:21.04,Default,T,0,0,0,,Hey babe!
Dialogue: 100,0:23:21.04,0:23:22.96,Default,K,0,0,0,,Where'd you pick {\i1}that{\i0} up?
Dialogue: 100,0:24:56.72,0:24:57.64,Default,T,0,0,0,,Miss Kobayashi!
Dialogue: 100,0:24:57.64,0:24:59.72,Default,T,0,0,0,,This time, tell me what you like!
Dialogue: 100,0:24:59.72,0:25:00.35,Default,K,0,0,0,,Maids.
Dialogue: 100,0:25:00.35,0:25:02.14,Default,T,0,0,0,,You're talking about me, right?
Dialogue: 100,0:25:02.14,0:25:03.35,Default,K,0,0,0,,You're a little off.
Dialogue: 100,0:25:03.35,0:25:04.35,Default,T,0,0,0,,What else?
Dialogue: 100,0:25:04.35,0:25:05.23,Default,K,0,0,0,,Peace.
Dialogue: 100,0:25:05.23,0:25:06.81,Default,T,0,0,0,,I guess I'm all you need, then!
Dialogue: 100,0:25:06.81,0:25:08.98,Default,K,0,0,0,,You're a little off there too.
