Dialogue: 10,0:02:29.96,0:02:31.42,OP-E,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(0,120)\blur4\an5\pos(960.00,148.00)}Tell me, how did I get here?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:31.42,0:02:33.38,OP-E,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(120,120)\blur4\an5\pos(960.00,148.00)}I only made one tiny-winey mistake
Dialogue: 10,0:02:33.38,0:02:37.09,OP-E,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(210,0)\blur4\an5\pos(960.00,148.00)}and now I'm at a ta-la-la ta-la-ta total loss
Dialogue: 10,0:02:37.09,0:02:38.59,OP-E,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur4\an5\pos(960.00,148.00)}Why now of all times
Dialogue: 10,0:02:38.59,0:02:40.39,OP-E,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur4\an5\pos(960.00,148.00)}did I grow a spine and stick around?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:40.39,0:02:43.93,OP-E,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur4\an5\pos(960.00,148.00)}Somehow I've been taken by whimsy
Dialogue: 10,0:02:43.93,0:02:46.18,OP-E,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur4\an5\pos(960.00,148.00)}with no choice but to sing along
Dialogue: 10,0:02:46.18,0:02:49.52,OP-E,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(0,120)\blur4\an5\pos(960.00,148.00)}That's just how it is at first,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:49.52,0:02:53.19,OP-E,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(300,0)\blur4\an5\pos(960.00,148.00)}feeling like you're not in control
Dialogue: 10,0:02:53.19,0:02:56.74,OP-E,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(0,120)\blur4\an5\pos(960.00,148.00)}But if you open up and listen...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:56.74,0:03:01.87,OP-E,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(180,0)\blur4\an5\pos(960.00,148.00)}that's your voice saying, "Come on! Let's go!"
Dialogue: 10,0:03:01.87,0:03:03.62,OP-E,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur4\an5\pos(960.00,148.00)}(Anywhere is fine!)
Dialogue: 10,0:03:03.62,0:03:10.50,OP-E,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(0,160)\blur4\an5\pos(960.00,148.00)}I have the courage to become your wings
Dialogue: 10,0:03:10.50,0:03:14.05,OP-E,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(120,120)\blur4\an5\pos(960.00,148.00)}I'll take on the world without any fear
Dialogue: 10,0:03:14.05,0:03:17.97,OP-E,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(220,0)\blur4\an5\pos(960.00,148.00)}as long as I feel this magic
Dialogue: 10,0:03:17.97,0:03:24.76,OP-E,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(120,120)\blur4\an5\pos(960.00,148.00)}A bouquet for this unfamiliar world,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:24.76,0:03:28.64,OP-E,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(170,0)\blur4\an5\pos(960.00,148.00)}wrapped up together in this moment
Dialogue: 10,0:03:28.64,0:03:30.31,OP-E,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur4\an5\pos(960.00,148.00)}We communicate on different levels,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:30.31,0:03:32.19,OP-E,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur4\an5\pos(960.00,148.00)}but it doesn't bother me one bit
Dialogue: 10,0:03:32.19,0:03:34.61,OP-E,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(0,240)\blur4\an5\pos(960.00,148.00)}so long as this peace lasts forevermore
