Comment: 0,0:02:29.96,0:02:31.42,OP-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur4}Tell me, how did I get here?
Comment: 0,0:02:31.42,0:02:33.38,OP-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur4}I only made one tiny-winey mistake
Comment: 0,0:02:33.38,0:02:37.09,OP-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur4}and now I'm at a ta-la-la ta-la-ta total loss
Comment: 0,0:02:37.09,0:02:38.59,OP-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur4}Why now of all times
Comment: 0,0:02:38.59,0:02:40.39,OP-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur4}did I grow a spine and stick around?
Comment: 0,0:02:40.39,0:02:43.93,OP-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur4}Somehow I've been taken by whimsy
Comment: 0,0:02:43.93,0:02:46.18,OP-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur4}with no choice but to sing along
Comment: 0,0:02:46.18,0:02:49.52,OP-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur4}That's just how it is at first,
Comment: 0,0:02:49.52,0:02:53.19,OP-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur4}feeling like you're not in control
Comment: 0,0:02:53.19,0:02:56.74,OP-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur4}But if you open up and listen...
Comment: 0,0:02:56.74,0:03:01.87,OP-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur4}that's your voice saying, "Come on! Let's go!"
Comment: 0,0:03:01.87,0:03:03.62,OP-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur4}(Anywhere is fine!)
Comment: 0,0:03:03.62,0:03:10.50,OP-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur4}I have the courage to become your wings
Comment: 0,0:03:10.50,0:03:14.05,OP-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur4}I'll take on the world without any fear
Comment: 0,0:03:14.05,0:03:17.97,OP-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur4}as long as I feel this magic
Comment: 0,0:03:17.97,0:03:24.76,OP-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur4}A bouquet for this unfamiliar world,
Comment: 0,0:03:24.76,0:03:28.64,OP-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur4}wrapped up together in this moment
Comment: 0,0:03:28.64,0:03:30.31,OP-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur4}We communicate on different levels,
Comment: 0,0:03:30.31,0:03:32.19,OP-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur4}but it doesn't bother me one bit
Comment: 0,0:03:32.19,0:03:34.61,OP-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur4}so long as this peace lasts forevermore
