Comment: 0,0:23:38.93,0:23:41.27,ED-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\an5\move(960,162,960,-316,2030,2330)\c&H23AAFF&}and give my all to serve you
Comment: 0,0:23:41.02,0:23:43.36,ED-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\an5\move(960,1284,960,162,0,310)\c&HEBAFE9&}We'll spend all our time together,
