Comment: 0,0:23:45.44,0:23:47.65,ED-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\c&H9B48B8&}So sweet and filling
Comment: 0,0:23:47.65,0:23:49.94,ED-E,clipout,0,0,0,karaoke,{\c&H9B48B8&}Pure bliss~ {_ln choose the punctuation}{tildes cuz Tohru's a huge weeb}{ln you clown this is elma} Seconds, please!
Comment: 0,0:23:50.07,0:23:52.24,ED-E,clipin,0,0,0,karaoke,{\c&HF7CD89&}Come on, snuggle with me
Comment: 0,0:23:52.24,0:23:56.33,ED-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\c&HF7CD89&}Get over here and quit being a tease!
Comment: 0,0:23:56.53,0:23:58.79,ED-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\c&HEBAFE9&}Why must the rules be so strict?
Comment: 0,0:23:58.79,0:24:01.00,ED-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\c&HF7CD89&}It's like my heart's bound in chains
Comment: 0,0:24:01.00,0:24:05.46,ED-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,What an inferior and foolish system of values
Comment: 0,0:24:05.46,0:24:07.67,ED-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\c&H9B48B8&}It just isn't any good
Comment: 0,0:24:07.67,0:24:09.63,ED-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\c&H23AAFF&}These "morals" of yours are worthless
Comment: 0,0:24:09.63,0:24:13.47,ED-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\c&H23AAFF&}Ah~ I wanna eradicate it all!
Comment: 0,0:24:14.18,0:24:19.02,ED-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,Let's do some interspecies communication
Comment: 0,0:24:19.02,0:24:23.27,ED-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,and eclipse the world with our passion
Comment: 0,0:24:23.27,0:24:27.90,ED-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,A whole week of that?
Comment: 0,0:24:27.90,0:24:32.49,ED-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,It'd be more precious than an eternity
Comment: 0,0:24:32.49,0:24:35.91,ED-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,The past and the future don't mean a thing
Comment: 0,0:24:35.91,0:24:38.03,ED-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,Simply being here right now
Comment: 0,0:24:38.03,0:24:40.29,ED-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,with the people here right now
Comment: 0,0:24:40.29,0:24:41.25,ED-E,nooffset,0,0,0,karaoke,is what I love!
Comment: 0,0:24:43.42,0:24:45.63,ED-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,interspecies communication
Comment: 0,0:24:47.84,0:24:50.01,ED-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,supersimple imagination
Comment: 0,0:24:50.01,0:24:54.97,ED-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,Eliminate common sense and you're in paradise! Paradise!
